----

Corporate patent lawyers and lawyers in general wield great influence in the United States.  They have, without much regard for US national interest, been using the muscle of the US government in order to press other countries into removing all limits on patentable subject matter. Join [[FfiiUsEn| FFII US]] to make your voice heard.

